snippet.title: Alf's World of Words gameplay (PC Game, 1988)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Alf's World of Words, Dos PC game produced by Vision Software in 1988 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/alf-s-world-of-words/13573/
Alf's World of Words is an excellent edutainment game starring one of America's most famous children TV characters. It's a special game for preschoolers, to teach them the alphabet and basic words.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:

Spell It Plus! - https://youtu.be/EjvfE1Smr0I
